WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:03:17.185
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:03:17.186 --> 00:03:42.976
We're so thankful for his presence already here. I feel him, I feel the glory in the house, and I'm so grateful for every single one of you that have come out tonight to pray with us.

00:03:42.977 --> 00:03:51.697
In just a couple of minutes, we already have almost 1,500 people here, and I'm just so grateful for every single one of you that come out and take prayer seriously.

00:03:51.698 --> 00:04:03.040
We have a lot of work to do, so we'll get right to it. I want to go over some of the things that the Lord showed us over the last prayer time we had.

00:04:03.041 --> 00:04:11.262
Over the last couple of videos, some of the things that we have seen by the leading of the Holy Spirit are in the news now.

00:04:11.263 --> 00:04:20.715
I want to give all glory and honor to Jesus that I have a treasure in an earthen vessel, that the excellency of the power is known of him and not of me.

00:04:20.716 --> 00:04:27.801
I want to tell you all immediately, everything that we see, everything we do, we give all to the glory of God.

00:04:27.802 --> 00:04:37.043
It's all his glory—none of me and all of him. And so I'm excited when we see what we've been praying for, and it's in the news today.

00:04:37.044 --> 00:04:46.462
I said, 'We don't pray the news; we pray for what's coming in the news.'We are the news, and people will come here to get the news first.

00:04:46.463 --> 00:04:51.422
I believe in being prophetic and accurate and not being flaky in these last days.

00:04:51.423 --> 00:04:56.072
If I miss it, I'll be the first one to tell you; I'm just human.

00:04:56.073 --> 00:05:03.296
We all have missed it and we all try our best to be accurate. But you know what? We're flesh.

00:05:03.297 --> 00:05:10.634
That pipe sometimes gets a little cocky, and we have to make sure that we keep our thermostat right so that we don't lead people astray.

00:05:10.635 --> 00:05:20.332
My heart is always to do right. I want to tell you thank you for being here, and thank you for trusting us to pray with us and to do things we're doing.

00:05:20.333 --> 00:05:29.252
It's all Jesus. So, let's go over some of the news real quick. We'll talk about it and see what we found.

00:05:29.253 --> 00:05:34.827
Braden said, 'Dad, did you see what happened today in the news concerning NASA?'NASA?

00:05:34.828 --> 00:05:43.310
How many of y'all? Go ahead and play the clip of what the Lord showed us. Do you have that ready? Yes.

00:05:43.311 --> 00:05:53.110
I want you just to play some of the things the Lord showed us about the moon.

00:05:53.111 --> 00:06:01.651
Excuse me. This was on December the 2nd of last year. Go ahead.

00:06:01.652 --> 00:06:09.820
'I hear them say they're going to go to the moon. They want to go to the moon.

00:06:09.821 --> 00:06:17.990
There's a base on the moon. I kid you not. I see a structure. I see a structure.

00:06:17.991 --> 00:06:24.604
How is that even possible? Is that it, Lord? What am I seeing on this space race?

00:06:24.605 --> 00:06:33.247
Space race? Yes. Space race.'Okay, so in the space race, I saw a thing on the moon's surface.

00:06:33.248 --> 00:06:44.895
It looked like a dome with lights on it. Now, I don't know what I was looking at, but it looked like box windows of some kind of light.

00:06:44.896 --> 00:06:55.562
They had made some kind of base—trying to make a base to escape the earth, to get away from all the drama going down here and go to the moon.

00:06:55.563 --> 00:07:09.089
I saw a base that looked like pods. They looked like little places, but people were trying to fly up there to stay on the moon. I was like, 'What is this?'So, a new space race.

00:07:09.090 --> 00:07:29.922
And I saw—which, if it was legitimate the first time, I don't understand why this would be such a big deal the second time—but it was a space race to get to the moon again with actual astronauts landing on the moon.

00:07:29.923 --> 00:07:41.344
I saw actual stuff happening with that. A real something. I thought that was interesting because these spaceships were different.

00:07:41.345 --> 00:07:53.613
I was like, 'What is going on with this?'In the vision, I could see that it was so clear. I saw the space race.

00:07:53.614 --> 00:08:03.866
Next, I see technological advancements, and it will be shock and awe and the uncovering of the technological advancements that the United States possesses.

00:08:03.867 --> 00:08:19.676
Some will say it looks like alien technology. Even in the days ahead, there will be even greater things because of quantum computing.

00:08:19.677 --> 00:08:29.399
There's a breakthrough concerning fuel—a breakthrough for a fuel with water.

00:08:29.400 --> 00:08:47.047
The splitting of what you would consider an atom. Endless energy, I hear the Lord say, is coming—greater than petrol. The blue light.

00:08:47.048 --> 00:09:02.745
It's by mathematical equations that they're going to achieve this new energy that is greater than the splitting of an atom, like nuclear.

00:09:02.746 --> 00:09:11.332
It's greater than nuclear. And it will be in jets—clean energy.

00:09:11.333 --> 00:09:19.764
I hear clean energy better than fossil fuels is coming with the splitting of new energy.

00:09:19.765 --> 00:09:26.614
They're about to harness it. They're about to harness this new blue energy.

00:09:26.615 --> 00:09:33.465
And when it does, it spins with bubbles with great electricity.

00:09:33.466 --> 00:09:47.232
It looks like pulses. That is blue light and it's split. I see the bubbles in it in a laboratory with water all around it.

00:09:47.233 --> 00:09:52.153
The mathematical equation is even greater than what they've had before.

00:09:52.154 --> 00:10:01.548
You know, they say hydrogen fusion, this hydrogen molecule, a hydrogen engine. It is something greater for jets.

00:10:01.549 --> 00:10:11.837
And they're trying to say, 'Well, we'll use it for...'I hear it's Elon for going to Mars for long, sustainable energy.

00:10:11.838 --> 00:10:25.892
Remember I told you a new space race is coming, and I said don't try to do things on the moon. And it's going to be like I saw—and I told you, I saw the base.

00:10:25.893 --> 00:10:32.712
It was in the picture, and I saw they're going to try to do things on the moon with this new technology.

00:10:32.713 --> 00:10:41.082
It's a blue energy and it's better than nuclear. Okay. So then we hear what happened today. Do you have the video? Yeah. Go ahead and play.

00:10:41.083 --> 00:10:46.972
'We're going to hit pause on the gateway, which was a space station designed to orbit above the moon.

00:10:46.973 --> 00:10:51.932
Right. You don't want to orbit above the moon. We want to be on the moon.

00:10:51.933 --> 00:10:58.132
We want to build the base. We want to interact with the regolith. We want to do in-situ resource manufacturing.

00:10:58.133 --> 00:11:01.852
We want to test out mobility on the surface to power communications.

00:11:01.853 --> 00:11:07.122
We want to build President Trump's moon base that he called for in the national space policy.

00:11:07.123 --> 00:11:11.772
We have the resources to do this. We have a lot of resources at NASA.

00:11:11.773 --> 00:11:16.112
We just need to move them in the needle-moving direction.'So they admitted it today.

00:11:16.113 --> 00:11:21.072
Isn't that amazing? The things we see in the spirit, they're talking about doing them now.

00:11:21.073 --> 00:11:26.962
And today they announced it. 'We want to build a moon base. We want to do all these things.

00:11:26.963 --> 00:11:34.092
We don't want to just orbit the moon; we want to build something on the moon.'And I said they're going to do it.

00:11:34.093 --> 00:11:40.602
I've seen it. I know how they do it. I watched how they do it. And so there's more clips here.

00:11:40.603 --> 00:11:44.632
'First, in the future, we will build the moon base in three phases.

00:11:44.633 --> 00:11:51.142
Phase one endeavors to support industry by moving from infrequent, bespoke efforts to a templated approach that will generate significant learning.

00:11:51.143 --> 00:12:08.192
Through experimentation, we will dramatically expand lunar landings through the CLPS and the LTV program, delivering rovers, instruments, and technology payloads that test mobility and power systems, such as working with international partners and industry on the production of RTGs and RHUs, communications, navigation, surface operations, and all the science payload that can be incorporated.

00:12:08.193 --> 00:12:15.012
Phase two transitions from experimentation to semi-habitable infrastructure and routine logistics, with the aim of supporting regular astronaut operations on the surface.

00:12:15.013 --> 00:12:20.592
It's at this point we anticipate seeing the significant contributions from our great partners like JAXA's pressurized rover.

00:12:20.593 --> 00:12:31.752
Phase three takes advantage of the affordable mass-to-surface capabilities that cargo HLS will inevitably provide in the years ahead and enables the permanent infrastructure necessary to sustain a human presence, such as Italy's proposed habitation module.

00:12:31.753 --> 00:12:34.022
The moon base will not appear overnight. We will invest approximately $20 billion over the next seven years and build it through dozens of missions, working together with commercial and international partners towards a deliberate and achievable plan.

00:12:34.023 --> 00:12:34.122
Just as there was Mercury and Gemini before Apollo, there will be an evolutionary path to building humanity's first permanent surface outpost beyond Earth, and we will take the world along with us as they follow along on the NASA moon base website and watch the assembly through lunar relay and observation satellites.'When the Lord tells us before the world gets to hear it, it's all to his glory.

00:12:34.123 --> 00:12:34.322
Isn't that neat? I said, 'Lord, you're talking to us, and we're hearing it over the course of the last eight or nine months or a year.'And it's accurate, what the Lord is showing us.

00:12:34.323 --> 00:12:34.522
And you say, 'Well, Brandon, that's kind of scary. Why are they doing all that?'Because the end is coming.

00:12:34.523 --> 00:12:34.822
You all have to understand. They see something. I told you I saw an asteroid coming.

00:12:34.823 --> 00:12:35.022
I saw them in meetings. The Lord allowed me to go to these meetings.

00:12:35.023 --> 00:12:35.222
I hear what they're saying. There is an object that is approaching Earth.

00:12:35.223 --> 00:12:35.322
And the Lord showed me mathematical equations all on this table.

00:12:35.323 --> 00:12:35.622
And he said their mathematical equations are wrong; it will hit Earth. It's in my word. It will not be avoided.

00:12:35.623 --> 00:12:35.722
But this object that they know is coming, they're trying to prepare, saying, 'The odds are in our favor.

00:12:35.723 --> 00:12:36.122
The odds are in our favor. It will not touch Earth.'They're wrong. It will. The Lord said this and he said, 'It's in my word.

00:12:36.123 --> 00:12:36.222
It's called Wormwood.'And many people do not realize the signs of the times.

00:12:36.223 --> 00:12:36.422
In the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ, it's all around us. I try to warn you all the time.

00:12:36.423 --> 00:12:36.522
I said, 'Lord, all the things that we talk about, everything in the accuracy of what we see...'We all see in part.

00:12:36.523 --> 00:12:36.622
And I believe that everybody has the ability, if you're a born-again Christian, to hear the voice of God for yourself.

00:12:36.623 --> 00:12:36.822
You don't need us. You just need the Holy Spirit, and you already have him.

00:12:36.823 --> 00:12:39.848
If you recognize him and invite him into your house, if you invite him into your temple...

00:12:39.849 --> 00:12:48.670
You know what his address is like? You have an address to your home. His address is your name. It's you. His address is you.

00:12:48.671 --> 00:12:57.575
He dwells on the inside of you, and most people don't even give him the time of day to even say, 'Welcome, Holy Spirit.

00:12:57.576 --> 00:13:04.253
How are you doing? How's your day? Let's be friends. Let's talk things. Show me the secret things.

00:13:04.254 --> 00:13:20.153
Show me the mysteries that no one else knows.'And if you treat him like a friend and not like some far-out religious object, he is an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:13:20.154 --> 00:13:25.450
But there are so many people that don't allow the Holy Spirit to invade them.

00:13:25.451 --> 00:13:36.065
You should allow him to take you over and say, 'Hey, I yield myself to you. I want you to become more real to me.

00:13:36.066 --> 00:13:42.210
I want to be wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.'And what people don't realize is he's a gentleman.

00:13:42.211 --> 00:13:51.769
He'll never force his way in on you. If he's knocking on your heart, he doesn't just shove the door open.

00:13:51.770 --> 00:14:01.423
He wants you to invite him. Day by day, just like I would go to somebody's house, I would knock on their door.

00:14:01.424 --> 00:14:06.435
Even if it was the second day and I was there the night before, you always knock.

00:14:06.436 --> 00:14:16.912
You're a gentleman. You don't just barge into their house. You knock and say, 'Hey, I'm here.'And that's the way he is.

00:14:16.913 --> 00:14:28.757
'Hey, I'm here. Will you allow me to lead you? Will you allow me to fill you?'Like that guy says, 'Fill my cup, Lord.'Why do I sing that song so much?

00:14:28.758 --> 00:14:33.782
'Fill my cup, Lord, I lift it up, Lord.'It's because we leak out.

00:14:33.783 --> 00:14:44.292
And the more we leak out, the more we have all this trash around us and the dark's getting darker, the more we have to remain filled.

00:14:44.293 --> 00:14:52.921
It's like my friend Billy Burke says, 'You let your full fight for you.'You have to let your full fight for you.

00:14:52.922 --> 00:14:58.563
If you're empty, you're not going to be able to resist the devil like you should.

00:14:58.564 --> 00:15:07.192
You must be filled and controlled by the Holy Ghost in these last days. So I just encourage you even more so to remain full.

00:15:07.193 --> 00:15:12.400
You don't need a YouTube channel to help you in your relationship with God.

00:15:12.401 --> 00:15:23.933
I might encourage you and we pray together, for many hands make light work, but you need to have an intimate relationship with God by yourself and you must find him.

00:15:23.934 --> 00:15:28.770
You're running out of time. It's time to stop playing church.

00:15:28.771 --> 00:15:37.180
Jesus Christ is coming. He's standing at the door. I'm telling you, I've seen vision after vision of him.

00:15:37.181 --> 00:15:42.565
He's coming, ladies and gentlemen. This dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:15:42.566 --> 00:15:47.180
Everything we know is about to accelerate at an even greater scale.

00:15:47.181 --> 00:15:58.464
As of April 1st, the Lord said, when Passover comes, the birthing pains will now double, even greater than what they were from Rosh Hashanah on the 23rd.

00:15:58.465 --> 00:16:08.219
It was six months, and he said this is another window and another acceleration of things is about to take place.

00:16:08.220 --> 00:16:18.380
But it won't just be with wars and rumors of wars. In Matthew 24, it talks about wars, earthquakes in divers places, plagues, and pestilence.

00:16:18.381 --> 00:16:24.258
But these are the beginning of sorrows. I want you to see what happened again today.

00:16:24.259 --> 00:16:28.541
I told you, we're about to see major asteroids all throughout the Earth.

00:16:28.542 --> 00:16:35.461
Things are going to be freaking people out because of fearful sights you will see that will bring you to your knees.

00:16:35.462 --> 00:16:41.458
He said, 'Brandon, I'm taking My hand off of certain things to shake the earth because they're asleep.

00:16:41.459 --> 00:16:57.981
They're not awake for what's about to take place, and they must know that this dispensation of grace is coming to an end, for I'm going to give them signs now in the heavens.'Remember when I told you that there was none of this?

00:16:57.982 --> 00:17:01.663
Now look what happened today—yesterday. Go ahead, play it.

00:17:01.664 --> 00:17:09.126
Look at them. Okay, well, go ahead and tell him. Yeah. See this one?

00:17:09.127 --> 00:17:13.600
This is California. They're falling. I told you, the rocks are coming.

00:17:13.601 --> 00:17:21.430
There's one right there. There's one right here. Where's this one? I think this is the same one. Boom!

00:17:21.431 --> 00:17:35.325
I said it will be so loud soon that it will break the glass out of your houses and your cars because it will be such a sonic boom and it will be coming so fast.

00:17:35.326 --> 00:17:42.714
And I said it will shake the buildings. That's Ohio. Do you see them?

00:17:42.715 --> 00:17:48.936
They're coming. And the Lord warned us. The second phase is upon us; it starts April 1st.

00:17:48.937 --> 00:17:57.103
It's already happening. The birthing pains, He said, will come. It will start to be out of what you see.

00:17:57.104 --> 00:18:03.913
You have wars and rumors of wars, and now we'll start to go to the signs of the heavens.

00:18:03.914 --> 00:18:10.230
Five major shakings, He said, will start to take place in the earth.

00:18:10.231 --> 00:18:18.034
What are those major shakings? He's going to shake the church. He's going to shake the heavens.

00:18:18.035 --> 00:18:22.122
He's going to shake the earth's crust with earthquakes and volcanoes.

00:18:22.123 --> 00:18:27.392
He's going to shake politics, and He's going to shake the finances.

00:18:27.393 --> 00:18:32.871
And then He said He's going to shake—what is that? All of them.

00:18:32.872 --> 00:18:35.220
That's all of politics, finances, the heavens, and the Earth.

00:18:35.221 --> 00:18:41.091
Yeah. And wars and rumors of wars, I believe, is one of the others.

00:18:41.092 --> 00:18:46.179
Five major shakings, but I want to show you these other ones.

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:51.658
Another one here: the Houston area. Right. So show this, just show that.

00:18:51.659 --> 00:18:55.851
That's good. I like that picture; pictures are good. Yeah, this is Houston.

00:18:55.852 --> 00:19:01.092
They're showing rocks falling through people's roofs. All of a sudden, all these rocks are coming to people's houses.

00:19:01.093 --> 00:19:06.070
This is happening, and it goes with what the Lord told us. And I told you it was coming.

00:19:06.071 --> 00:19:10.525
Even in prayer, we have documented proof of everything that I'm telling you.

00:19:10.526 --> 00:19:24.450
The Lord has warned us; this is coming. But He said it, and then He warned us that a lot of you will call it an Ichabod. What's going on with everything? It's an Ichabod.

00:19:24.451 --> 00:19:33.601
And the Lord said, 'It's not an Ichabod.'You consider bad things happening and shakings in the earth, and you say it's judgment.

00:19:33.602 --> 00:19:49.818
But I told you 1 Corinthians 5:5 and 2026 would come to a full head and it would go straight up and everybody's going to go, 'What's going on?'1 Corinthians 5:5: judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:19:49.819 --> 00:20:02.525
And He said, 'Many of you, because you've had such a shallow relationship with Me, when trials and tribulations hit your life...'He's yelled and yelled, and COVID was the first wave of the shaking.

00:20:02.526 --> 00:20:12.141
And people didn't wake up. They opened their eyes, and as we were praying last time, I saw a man on a bed—it looked like a plank—and he opened his eyes.

00:20:12.142 --> 00:20:18.080
And the Lord said, 'The church is about to open their eyes. The church is about to open their eyes, Brandon.

00:20:18.081 --> 00:20:23.793
They're asleep and they're about to open their eyes.'Why? Because I'm bringing the bride by My side.

00:20:23.794 --> 00:20:32.591
I'm shaking the bride. I'm waking the bride to bring her to My side. It's time for the church to wake up, and they're asleep.

00:20:32.592 --> 00:20:48.703
So He said, 'You're going to see some things, and many of you are not prepared.'And He said, 'Hard times will come to some.'But He said the ones that are prepared will be in the cleft of the rock.

00:20:48.704 --> 00:20:53.290
They'll be in the refuge, the secret place. But the others, some of you will go home early.

00:20:53.291 --> 00:20:57.622
Some of you are going to go home early. You need to hear what I'm telling you.

00:20:57.623 --> 00:21:04.758
If you're not listening to the voice of the Lord and where He tells you to be every single day—He says, 'Hey, you need to be here.

00:21:04.759 --> 00:21:16.163
You need to be there'—but that Holy Spirit inside of you, you say, 'I'm not going to listen to that; I want to go here.'It could be your last day on the earth because you didn't listen.

00:21:16.164 --> 00:21:24.158
You must know Psalm 91. You must know Psalm 23, but you must have an intimate relationship with Him in your heart, and you must hear Him.

00:21:24.159 --> 00:21:34.153
The Bible says, 'My sheep will hear My voice and a stranger's voice they'll not follow.'He's not trying to scare you; He's trying to prepare you, for perilous times are here.

00:21:34.154 --> 00:21:40.400
And if you don't listen to Him... He said, 'I don't want you to go to the mall today.

00:21:40.401 --> 00:21:49.525
I don't want you to go over there today,'because the people who heard the Lord not to go in the building on 9/11 are still here.

00:21:49.526 --> 00:21:56.076
Do you understand? Well, God, how come You didn't protect me? Brother Kenneth Hagin talked about a young man.

00:21:56.077 --> 00:22:01.692
They were up every night praying for this member of their church.

00:22:01.693 --> 00:22:06.059
Do you see these asteroids? They're all falling in the sky now.

00:22:06.060 --> 00:22:17.024
I know this is a lot of ring cameras and probably the same asteroid on some of them, but this is Ohio, and they're falling. Do you understand? And it's in the middle of the day.

00:22:17.025 --> 00:22:24.548
But Brother Hagin talked about a story one time, and he said that there was a young man—he was up interceding and they couldn't get a release.

00:22:24.549 --> 00:22:29.843
They couldn't get it. But they said, 'Lord, show what we're feeling concerning praying for this young man.

00:22:29.844 --> 00:22:37.376
Give him a dream of what he's supposed to—what we're warning about.'He was a congregation member.

00:22:37.377 --> 00:22:42.641
Well, he had a dream that night. And he worked on an oil derrick.

00:22:42.642 --> 00:22:57.029
He worked on the oil crew, and he saw that if he went up on this certain pole, the wire would come loose and it would sever his head. It would cut his head off.

00:22:57.030 --> 00:23:07.810
So he went to the foreman, the guy that was over the oil rig, and he told him—because the guy that was supposed to be there called in sick that day—and he said, 'Well, it's your second line.

00:23:07.811 --> 00:23:25.531
You're going to go up that pole and work and do this oil job.'He said, 'Now I have a lead—I just feel I had a dream last night, and in my dream, the Lord told me that if I went up that pole, I saw my decapitation, and I can't go up that pole.

00:23:25.532 --> 00:23:34.725
I can't go up and do that job today.'There was a Baptist guy that was sitting next to him and he said, 'Oh, I'm not superstitious.

00:23:34.726 --> 00:23:43.096
I'll go up there and do it,'kind of making fun of him. He shot up there, and a couple minutes later, they're all on the job site.

00:23:43.097 --> 00:23:53.868
But five minutes into it, he's up there and all of a sudden—the man said he won't do it because he was the Holy Ghost-filled man, led and controlled by the Holy Ghost.

00:23:53.869 --> 00:24:03.013
He went to Brother Hagin's church and was on the ground working, and as he was working, that line broke and severed that man's head off.

00:24:03.014 --> 00:24:12.168
And that head hit that man that didn't go up, and it went into his back as he was laying on the ground working.

00:24:12.169 --> 00:24:21.799
True story. The man's head was severed, fell on the man that was Holy Ghost-filled in his back. Both were born-again Christians.

00:24:21.800 --> 00:24:40.043
Both love the Lord, but one was yielded to the Holy Spirit by praying in tongues and being filled and controlled by the Holy Ghost, and one was just like, 'I'm not all the way filled; I'm not going to be all in.'Do you understand?

00:24:40.044 --> 00:24:46.866
Was it that God loved the one more than the other? No, I don't believe that. God loves us all.

00:24:46.867 --> 00:24:51.975
And I believe He loved the Baptist, and I believe He loves the Pentecostal.

00:24:51.976 --> 00:24:58.681
But it takes following His voice in these last days to make sure we're still here the next day.

00:24:58.682 --> 00:25:06.092
We cannot buck and say, 'Holy Spirit, I can hear You on some things and not hear You on others'for what's coming.

00:25:06.093 --> 00:25:10.739
